x4freetext: 2 mm thick surface-barrier detectors
The targets were prepared by vacuum evaporation of
isotopically enriched oxides. To get a good resolution,
the thickness of the target was limited to about
150 mug/cm**2, evaporated onto 25 mug/cm**2 carbon
backings.
